					<box></box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
						<font size="12"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Before making payment please ensure that there are no recoveries due from the individual.
                                                                                                                                                                       The DCRG is debitable under A-Expenditure from Revenue Account_V.Pension and Gratuity charges (ii) Gratuity.

The acquittance of the applicant may be obtained on the reverse of the order sent to the applicant with Re.1 Revenue stamp. The applicant is being informed of the issue of this order separately.

This order is issued subject to recovery of all dues from the retiring person before settlement of death benefits and if any dues are found to be recoverable from the retired person at a later date, the person who furnished the ‘no due’ certificate will be held responsible and action will be taken against him and he will be held liable for the unrecovered amount if any.

Before making payment it should be ensured that all the dues to TWAD Board and others i.e. Thrift Society Recovery, Bank loan recovery etc. if any are effected from his pensionary benefits.

Please acknowledge the receipt of this order and intimate the payment of gratuity with Cheque No. and date.
]]></text>
				</staticText>
